                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The 4 person agro rule ONLY applies to CHARMED PETS. If you have a summoned pet, it does not matter how many people are on the agro list. The only things that matter in that situation are:
<br />

<br />
Are any PCs in melee range of the mob? If so, pet wont hold agro.
<br />

<br />
and 2
<br />

<br />
Does the pet have enough agro generated to hold it? If not, just like a warrior, you will out taunt it.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Desseray Lokheart &lt;Frayed Knot&gt;
<br />
70 Coercer - The Rathe</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
